headline: MarketAxess to Participate in the Morgan Stanley U.S. Financials Conference
summary: NEW YORK, June 03, 2025--MarketAxess Holdings Inc. (Nasdaq: MKTX), the operator of a leading electronic trading platform for fixed-income securities, today announced that Ilene Fiszel Bieler, Chief Financial Officer, will participate in the Morgan Stanley U.S. Financials Conference on June 10, 2025.
